cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.SE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): This paper proposes a hardware architecture for a novel algorithm, which can be considered an emerging technology. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper specifically discusses the hardware architecture for the algorithm, making this category a likely fit. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The proposed system has three parts with different functionality, which can be seen as a control system. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The single iteration algorithm is a new algorithm for signal reconstruction, which can be considered a data structure and algorithm problem. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): Although the paper focuses on hardware architecture, it also discusses the realization of blocks for which there are no standard components in FPGA, which can be seen as a software engineering problem.
